  <h1>A8 — Insecure Deserialization</h1>
  <p class="muted">Executing or trusting deserialized data from untrusted sources can lead to code execution.</p>
  <h3>Mitigations</h3>
  <ul><li>Avoid using insecure deserializers for untrusted data (e.g., pickle).</li><li>Use safe formats (JSON) and validate schema.</li></ul>
  <h3>Where to patch</h3>
  <p>Search for uses of Python <code>pickle</code> or raw eval on data inputs.</p>
